This frame contains adjectives and nouns that describe the truth or sincerity of communication. These words, analogously to behaver-evaluating words, can apply either to Speakers or to the Messages they produce. They can occur with about-PPs expressing Topic.
Evelyn was candid with me about the party.

blunt.a, bluntness.n, candid.a, candour.n, circumspect.a, coy.a, devious.a, discreet.a, dishonest.a, disingenuous.a, earnest.a, earnestness.n, evasive.a, explicit.a, forthcoming.a, forthright.a, forthrightness.n, frank.a, honest.a, honesty.n, ingenuous.a, open.a, outspoken.a, secretive.a, sincere.a, straight.a, straightforward.a, truthful.a
